Text: Thankyou so much ....i'll stick with this show for a while , keep them coming !!

You can only stick with the show for one more week as the Season Finale airs on Oct 12th.

John Noble had to go back to doing Fringe, which dammit I love that show!

I guess this was the season finale.  

No more Dark Matters unless Science Channel comes back with a season 2.
